事<br />\n切完係舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c1a56edca37b478849063b5a6b5b4210f6a37c","tid":801490,"uid":89637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:23:14.000Z","msg":"我都試過 果陣腫到個喉嚨丁同則邊痴埋咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗三次醫生最後都係要入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吊咗三日水再瘋狂食抗生素同藥一個星期後先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cabf0020256ab2c85ea064f49546eece12b81d1","tid":801490,"uid":38781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd2f26beeee7d3ee95340045773b68bbc72caf1d","tid":801490,"uid":21224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf30ed256cc65450ee94e8fae42460dbab8ea92c","tid":801490,"uid":11695,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a9dfbffc86c14b8662a131e2493f463e34f94355","tid":801490,"uid":21224,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"睇左啦 醫生淨係開左5日抗生素俾我 食左2日都無好過。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"抗生素唔係止痛藥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可能有抗藥性，食完唔好就返去醫生度同佢講"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"如果可以 我想直接打針 但個醫生唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:30:34.000Z","msg":"邊有針打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 流感咩。抗生素係一個療程咁食，食到尾兩日睇下點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df4573f59db431ac41dbeb5bfe273364fbe7973","tid":801490,"uid":175835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"我睇開果間有藥直接用棉花棒幫你搽 ，5日好反哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb9a5a3acef93d28fb7d258268a5a40edf9234f","tid":801490,"uid":107382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s